features:

    *give instructor power to accept or reject students registering for there course
    -send email to instructor when a student asks for permission to register to there course
    -notify student that they have been accepted/rejected from registering to a course

    * a more intuitive way to inform students that they have to click on there rehearsal for them to submit it

    features for feedback:
    -attach concepts to lesson to grade by concepts the rehearsals students submit
    -grading system with the concepts
    -students needs to have a side bar while reviewing feedbacks where they will see the concepts they have grasp and the ones they need to work on
    -feedback self evaluation, students review themselves based on the concepts the lesson is teaching.
